            . I am an officer. I went to the prisoner's lodging, and saw him; I told him the watch had been stolen, and I should search - he said, "You are welcome to search my box, here is my key;" he was in bed: I searched his clothes, and in his watch pocket, I found this duplicate and ten others - he got out of bed, fell on his knees, and said, "I hope you will forgive me, I did it from distress;" he had not a farthing of money.</p>
